{"id": "sos025", "name": "Audio_???_702_12_17", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "We're here. The signal's thirty meters below the surface.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "That sly fox... what's he doing here?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Whatever the case, he's definitely up to something. He definitely let us discover the remains of this Shelter on purpose.\nEverybody, be on guard! Big B, Jackal, and Lucy get into an A formation, you're coming with me. The others await orders here. Pay attention to exits. Don't let anything go in or out.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Squad Member"], "content": "Got it!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Move out.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "Signals straight ahead, ten meters, nine... eight...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "No target in our field of vision...\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Shhh! Listen. What's that noise?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["UI_Click", "Sensor"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "!?\nThat noise……! <font size=\"3.6\">Quick, get down!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Squad Member"], "content": "!?!?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "Explosion"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "WAH!!!!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Captain! You good!?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "<i>...*cough...*cough... </i>I'm fine! Those rocks are blocking the path... Retain formation and do not move from your position!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "S***! My hand...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "Jackal? You alright?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "It's nothing, just a scratch. Damn... I'm gonna kill him...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "They ordered us to keep him alive...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "I don't give s***! Hey! Bambi, what's going on? You find him?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Bambi? You deaf?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... Duped\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Eyy!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "It's just the watch, tied to a remote control car. We've been tricked.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">F***!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "...? What is this place? A storage unit?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "Connect"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>Good afternoon, Mr. Sagar. Ah, based on your progress, you should've been here at noon. Hope I didn't underestimate you.</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>Forgive me for making your plan get a little out of control. Looks like I have a bit of reputation in Node 13.\nThis message is for you only. If things didn't go as I planned, please ask those around to leave before continuing with this message.</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>Would you like to know how I'd know you'd be separated from the others?</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>Hehe... If you were to catch a target alive down here, based on the geographic conditions, I'm guessing you'd use an A formation with you in the lead... Or perhaps a C formation? That way, no matter what happens, you'd be best suited to deal with it.</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>If that's the case, when that sensor triggered the explosive, it should \"just so happened\" to split you and your team, leaving you here alone. How do you like my masterpiece? Hope I didn't injure anyone.</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "This guy, he's even got our formation down... Hmph. Not bad.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>Excuse me, although I truly enjoy playing with you all, I've got something more important to attend to. I haven't been here for some time now.</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>Why did I choose this location? It's not because I recall our first meeting with delight, though that is indeed one of the reasons.\n... Mr. Sagar, I never had the chance to tell you...</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>The truth you've been searching for this whole time, lies at the end of this hallway.</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>If I told you, that'd be boring, wouldn't it? Do you see the circulation vent on the ceiling above you?</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>At your height, it may be a bit difficult to grab on, but if you get up there, you'll get to your comrades in no time. You may leave this place, and continue to track me.</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>But if you have even the slightest interest in what I said... Please, walk straight ahead.\nPlease, don't worry. I sincerely promise you that this is not a trap. It won't cost you anything to take a look before leaving.</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Hey! Bambi! We can't get into the circulation vent, but it looks like you'll fit. Come on, get back here, or we can send in Mrs. Freeze.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Bambi? What are you doing? Respond!\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "... I told you, remain in position and await orders.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "Captain? Where are you going?\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Don't act on your own! You hear me!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "This is an order. Give me ten minutes.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "S***... Mrs. Freeze, I'll lift you up. Get in there.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "... Got it!\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ついたな。\n信号はここの地下13メートルから発信されてる。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "あのキツネ……ここに戻ってきてどうするってんだ？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "わざわざ、俺たちがあの人を見つけたShelterに戻ってくるなんて、何か裏があるに違いない。\n全員警戒態勢！ビッグB、ジャッカル、Lucy、フォーメーションAだ。\n他の者は入り口を見張っていろ。\n何者も通すなよ！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小隊の隊員"], "content": "はっ！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "行くぞ。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "信号まであと10メートル、9……8……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "ターゲットがいない……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "しっ！聞け、何の音だ？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["UI_Click", "センサー"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "！？\nこれは……！<font size=\"3.6\">伏せろ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小隊の隊員"], "content": "！？！？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆発"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "うわ！！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長！無事！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ゴホッゴホッ……大丈夫だ！\n岩に道をふさがれてしまったな……\nフォーメーションを崩さずその場で待機！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "くそ！手が……！\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "ジャッカル、大丈夫か？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "なんでもねぇよ。\nかすり傷だ。\nくそ……殺す……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "生きて捕まえるのが俺たちの任務だぞ……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "俺様には関係ねぇ！\nおい！バンビ！どうなんだよ！\nいたのか？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "バンビ？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……ハメられた。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "はぁ！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "ここには遠隔コントロールできる車とそこに縛られた時計しかない。\n騙されたんだ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">くそ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……？これはなんだ？ストレージユニット？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "接続"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>こんにちは、Mr. Sagar。\n君たちの優秀さからすると、ここにたどり着いたのはお昼ごろかね？\n外れてなければいいが。</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>君たちの作戦をムダにしてしまってすまないね。\n私はNode13では多少なりとも人望があるのだよ。\nこれは、君だけに残すメッセージだ。\nもし私の予想が外れ、君の他に誰かいるのなら、彼らにはいったん退席を願いたい。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>なぜ君が一人なのが分かったのか知りたいかね？</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>はは、簡単さ。\n私を生け捕りにするならば、この地形的に君は君を先頭としたフォーメーションA……もしくはフォーメーションCで向かってくるだろう。\nそれが一番効率よく確実だからな。</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>ならば、センサーが反応して爆弾が爆発した時、ちょうど君一人を隊から離すことができるというわけさ。\n私の傑作は気に入っていただけたかな？\n君たちにケガを負わせていなければいいのだが。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "この男は、俺の使うフォーメーションまでぜんぶ……はっ、やっぱりすごいな。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>大変申し訳ない。\n君たちと遊びたい気持ちは山々なのだが、今私にはもっと大切な用事があってね。\nとうの昔に出て行かせてもらった。</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>この場所を選んだ理由は、ここは我々が初めて出会った思い出の場所だからさ。\nそれと……Mr. Sagar、これまで一度も君には話していなかったが……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>君が追い続けている真相は、この廊下の突きあたりに眠っている。</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>先に答えを言ってしまってはおもしろくないな。\n天上の通風孔が見えるか？</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>君の身長では手を届かせるのは難しいかもしれないが、そこを上れば仲間のもとへ帰れる。\nここを出て、私との追いかけっこをまた楽しめるというわけだ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>だが、君がもし少しでも私の先ほどの話に興味を引かれたのなら……先に進むといい。\n大丈夫。これは罠ではない。\n見届けてから出て行っても、君には何の損失もないだろう。</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "おい！バンビ！\n上の通風孔、俺らは入れねぇ！\nでもお前ならいけるだろ？\n早くこっち来い！\n氷の女王様をそっちに送るんでもいいぜ！\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "バンビ？なにしてんだ？\n応えろ！\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……さっきも言った通り、そこで待機だ。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長？どこへ？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "また単独行動か！？\nいい加減にしろよてめぇ！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "これは命令だ。\n10分待て。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "くそ……氷の女王様乗れ。\n付いて行くんだ。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……わかった！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "到了。訊號在地下十三公尺處。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "那個老狐狸……又繞回這邊做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "總之肯定有詐，刻意回到我們當初撿到他的 Shelter 遺跡。\n全體戒備！大 B、豺狼、Lucy 呈 A 隊形跟著我，Gary 你帶其他人在這邊待命，留意出入口動向，別讓任何東西進出。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小隊成員"], "content": "了解！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "前進。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "訊號前方十公尺、九……八……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "視野內沒有目標……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "噓！聽，什麼聲音？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["UI_Click", "感應器"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "！？\n這個聲音……！<font size=\"3.6\">快趴下！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小隊成員"], "content": "！？！？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆炸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哇！！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長！沒事嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "咳咳……沒事！石頭擋住路了……你們保持陣型待在原地別動！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "靠！我的手……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "豺狼？還好吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "沒事，擦傷而已。該死……我要殺了他……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "上面命令我們活捉……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "老子才不管！喂！斑比，到底怎樣？看見他沒？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？啞了？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……上當了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "吭！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "只有手錶而已，綁在一台遙控車上，我們被騙了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Fxxk！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……？這是什麼？儲存單元？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "連線"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>午安，Mr. Sagar。啊，以你們的進度來說抵達這邊的時間應該是中午吧？希望我沒有低估你。</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>很抱歉讓你們的計畫落空了，我在 Node 13 還是小有人望的。\n這段訊息是只留給你一個人的。如果情況不如我預期我也希望你把旁邊的人支開再播放。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>想知道為什麼我會知道你跟他們分開了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>呵呵，如果要以活捉為目標進到這裡逮我，以這個地形來說我猜你應該會使用以你帶頭的 A 陣型……或 C 陣型吧？這樣無論什麼突發狀況都能最有效應付。</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>那樣的話觸發到感應式炸彈的時機應該恰巧把你們隔開了，所以你現在是獨自一人。還喜歡我的傑作嗎？希望沒有弄傷你們。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "這傢伙，連我們的陣型都……哼，果然很厲害。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>失禮了，雖然也很想跟你們玩玩，但我現在有更重要的事情要處理，人老早就不在這了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>至於為什麼選在這個地點呢？可不是我懷念起了我們的第一次相遇，雖然也是原因之一……Mr. Sagar，我一直沒有機會告訴你……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>一直以來你所追求的真相，就在這條走廊的盡頭。</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>先說出來就不有趣了，看到天花板上的通風口了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>以你的身高可能很難勾到，不過上去的話就能順利回到夥伴身邊，離開這裡，繼續追捕我了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>但若你對我說的稍微有點興趣……就請往前走吧。\n請放心，我向你保證這絕對不是陷阱。看完後再離開對你也沒有任何損失。</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "喂！斑比！上面的通風口，我們都鑽不進去，但是你可以吧？快點回來。或是讓冰沙妹過去找你也可以。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？你在幹嘛啊？回話！\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我說了，你們待在原地待命。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長？你要去哪？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "又想獨自行動嗎？不要鬧啦！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "這是命令，等我十分鐘。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Sxxt……冰沙妹，我蹬妳上去，跟過去。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……好！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "도착했다. 신호는 지하 13미터 쪽에서 보내오고 있다.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "그 늙은 여우 녀석이....여기로 돌아와서 또 뭔 짓을 꾸미려고?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "분명 뭔가 꿍꿍이가 있겠지. 일부러 우리가 처음 그 녀석을 주웠던 Shelter 유적으로 돌아온 것을 보면 말이야.\n전원 경계 태세! B 형, 울프, Lucy, 포메이션 A 대형으로 나를 따라와.\n남은 사람은 입구를 감시하고 있어. 누구도 들어오게 하지 마.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["소대원"], "content": "알겠습니다!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "들어간다!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "신호 전방 10미터...9....8...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "타깃이 시야에 안 보인다......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "잠깐! 들어봐... 무슨 소리지?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["UI_Click", "감지음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "!?\n이 소리는......! <font size=\"3.6\">엎드려!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["소대원"], "content": "!?!?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "폭발"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "으악!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "대장! 괜찮아!?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "쿨럭 쿨럭......괜찮다! 바위에 길이 막혀버렸어... 대형을 유지한 채로 움직이지 말도록!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "제길... 내 손이......!\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "울프? 괜찮아?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "응, 괜찮아. 긁힌 것뿐이야.... 제길.... 아주 작살을 내주겠어...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "상부에서는 생포하라고 명령을 내렸......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "그딴 거 내 알 바 아니라고! 밤비! 어떻게 됐어? 그 녀석 찾았어?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "밤비?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......당했어.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "뭐!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "시계밖에 없어.... 무선 RC 카에 묶인 상태로.... 속았어.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Fxxk! ! </font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......? 이건 뭐지? 저장 유닛?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "연결"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>좋은 아침입니다, Mr. Sagar. 아, 여러분의 수사 진행 속도라면 아마 지금쯤 오후가 됐으려나요? 제가 예측한 시간이 맞았으면 좋겠건만.</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>여러분의 작전을 헛수고로 만들어버린 점, 미안합니다.  Node 13에서는 이래 봬도 나름 인망이 두터운 편이라서.\n이 메시지는 오직 당신 한 사람한테 남기는 겁니다. 만약 제 예상이 어긋나서 옆에 누군가라도 있는 상황이라면, 그 사람들에게 물러나 있으라고 말씀해 주시죠.</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>제가 왜 당신을 다른 사람들과 떨어뜨려 놓으려고 하는지 아시는지?</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>하하하! 간단합니다.\n만약 제 생포가 목적이라면 분명 포메이션 A... 혹은 C대열로 진입을 했을 테죠? 확실히 어떤 충돌이 발생하더라도 응전이라도 일어날 경우에는 그것이 가장 효과적이었을 테니까.</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>그렇게 한다면, 센서 반응 폭탄이 터졌을 때, 당신 하나만 그 무리에서 떼어놓을 수 있다는 것이죠.\n어떻습니까? 제 작전이 마음에 들었는지?\n여러분에게 부상을 입히게 된 것은 아니었는지, 그건 아니었으면 좋겠군요.</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "이 녀석, 우리들 대형까지 전부 꿰뚫고....훗, 역시 대단한 녀석이군.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>매우 죄송하게 됐습니다.\n여러분과 놀고 싶은 마음은 굴뚝같지만, 지금 제게 더 중요한 볼일이 있는 상황이라, 이미 진작에 이곳을 떠난 상태이지요.</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>제가 이 장소를 선택한 이유는, 바로 이곳이 우리가 처음으로 만났던 추억의 장소이기 때문입니다.\n뭐, 그것도 여러 이유 중 하나이지만 ...... Mr. Sagar, 지금까지 단 한 번도 당신에게 말해주지 않은 것이 있죠...</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>당신이 계속 쫓고 있던 진실,\n이 복도 끝에 있습니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>미리 말씀드리면 재미가 떨어지긴 하지만, 천장에 통풍구가 보이실 겁니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>당신의 키로는 손에 닿는 것이 어려울지도 모르겠지만, 어쨌든 그곳으로 올라가면 동료들과 합류할 수 있을 겁니다. 그리고 이곳을 빠져나간 후, 다시 저와의 추적 놀이를 시작하실 수 있겠죠.</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>하지만, 만약 조금이라도 내가 방금 한 얘기에 흥미가 생겼다면, 앞으로 곧장 걸어가시면 됩니다.\n절대로 함정이 아니니까 안심하셔도 좋습니다.\n그 진실을 보고 그곳을 나가도 당신에게는 아무런 손해도 아닐 테니까요.</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "야! 밤비! 위에 통풍구, 우린 모두 못 들어가지만, 네 체격으로는 가능하겠지? 빨리 돌아오라고. 아니면 얼음 공주가 내려가도 될 것 같아!\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "밤비! 뭐하고 있는 거야! 어서 대답해!\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "......아까 말했듯이, 너희들은 그 자리에서 대기하고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "대장? 어디 가는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "또 개별 행동하려고? 작작 좀 하라고!\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "이건 명령이다.\n10분만 기다려줘.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Sxxt......얼음 공주, 내가 올려줄 테니가 네가 따라가봐.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "......알았어!\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "到了。訊號在地下十三公尺處。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "那個老狐狸……又繞回這邊做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "總之肯定有詐，刻意回到我們當初撿到他的 Shelter 遺跡。\n全體戒備！大 B、豺狼、Lucy 呈 A 隊形跟著我，Gary 你帶其他人在這邊待命，留意出入口動向，別讓任何東西進出。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小隊成員"], "content": "了解！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "前進。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "訊號前方十公尺、九……八……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "視野內沒有目標……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "噓！聽，什麼聲音？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["UI_Click", "感應器"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "！？\n這個聲音……！<font size=\"3.6\">快趴下！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小隊成員"], "content": "！？！？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆炸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哇！！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長！沒事嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "咳咳……沒事！石頭擋住路了……你們保持陣型待在原地別動！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "靠！我的手……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "豺狼？還好吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "沒事，擦傷而已。該死……我要殺了他……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "上面命令我們活捉……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "老子才不管！喂！斑比，到底怎樣？看見他沒？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？啞了？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……上當了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "吭！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "只有手錶而已，綁在一台遙控車上，我們被騙了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Fxxk！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……？這是什麼？儲存單元？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "連線"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>午安，Mr. Sagar。啊，以你們的進度來說抵達這邊的時間應該是中午吧？希望我沒有低估你。</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>很抱歉讓你們的計畫落空了，我在 Node 13 還是小有人望的。\n這段訊息是只留給你一個人的。如果情況不如我預期我也希望你把旁邊的人支開再播放。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>想知道為什麼我會知道你跟他們分開了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>呵呵，如果要以活捉為目標進到這裡逮我，以這個地形來說我猜你應該會使用以你帶頭的 A 陣型……或 C 陣型吧？這樣無論什麼突發狀況都能最有效應付。</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>那樣的話觸發到感應式炸彈的時機應該恰巧把你們隔開了，所以你現在是獨自一人。還喜歡我的傑作嗎？希望沒有弄傷你們。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "這傢伙，連我們的陣型都……哼，果然很厲害。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>失禮了，雖然也很想跟你們玩玩，但我現在有更重要的事情要處理，人老早就不在這了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>至於為什麼選在這個地點呢？可不是我懷念起了我們的第一次相遇，雖然也是原因之一……Mr. Sagar，我一直沒有機會告訴你……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>一直以來你所追求的真相，就在這條走廊的盡頭。</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>先說出來就不有趣了，看到天花板上的通風口了嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>以你的身高可能很難勾到，不過上去的話就能順利回到夥伴身邊，離開這裡，繼續追捕我了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>但若你對我說的稍微有點興趣……就請往前走吧。\n請放心，我向你保證這絕對不是陷阱。看完後再離開對你也沒有任何損失。</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "喂！斑比！上面的通風口，我們都鑽不進去，但是你可以吧？快點回來。或是讓冰沙妹過去找你也可以。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？你在幹嘛啊？回話！\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我說了，你們待在原地待命。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "隊長？你要去哪？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "又想獨自行動嗎？不要鬧啦！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "這是命令，等我十分鐘。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Sxxt……冰沙妹，我蹬妳上去，跟過去。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……好！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_03"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "到了。讯号在地下十三公尺处。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "那个老狐狸……又绕回这边做什么？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "总之肯定有诈，刻意回到我们当初捡到他的 Shelter 遗迹。\n全体戒备！大 B、豺狼、Lucy 呈 A 队形跟着我，Gary 你带其他人在这边待命，留意出入口动向，别让任何东西进出。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小队成员"], "content": "了解！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "前进。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快转»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "讯号前方十公尺、九……八……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "视野内没有目标……\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "嘘！听，什么声音？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["UI_Click", "感应器"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "！ ？\n这个声音……！ <font size=\"3.6\">快趴下！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小队成员"], "content": "！ ？ ！ ？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Explosion", "爆炸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "哇！ ！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "队长！没事吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "咳咳……没事！石头挡住路了……你们保持阵型待在原地别动！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "靠！我的手……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "豺狼？还好吧？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "没事，擦伤而已。该死……我要杀了他……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Bruno"], "content": "上面命令我们活捉……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "老子才不管！喂！斑比，到底怎样？看见他没？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？哑了？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……上当了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "吭！ ？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "只有手表而已，绑在一台遥控车上，我们被骗了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Fxxk！ ！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……？这是什么？储存单元？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Projection_UI", "连线"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>午安，Mr. Sagar。啊，以你们的进度来说抵达这边的时间应该是中午吧？希望我没有低估你。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>很抱歉让你们的计画落空了，我在 Node 13 还是小有人望的。\n这段讯息是只留给你一个人的。如果情况不如我预期我也希望你把旁边的人支开再播放。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>想知道为什么我会知道你跟他们分开了吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>呵呵，如果要以活捉为目标进到这里逮我，以这个地形来说我猜你应该会使用以你带头的 A 阵型……或 C 阵型吧？这样无论什么突发状况都能最有效应付。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>那样的话触发到感应式炸弹的时机应该恰巧把你们隔开了，所以你现在是独自一人。还喜欢我的杰作吗？希望没有弄伤你们。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "这家伙，连我们的阵型都……哼，果然很厉害。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>失礼了，虽然也很想跟你们玩玩，但我现在有更重要的事情要处理，人老早就不在这了。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>至于为什么选在这个地点呢？可不是我怀念起了我们的第一次相遇，虽然也是原因之一……Mr. Sagar，我一直没有机会告诉你……</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>一直以来你所追求的真相，就在这条走廊的尽头。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……！ ？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>先说出来就不有趣了，看到天花板上的通风口了吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>以你的身高可能很难勾到，不过上去的话就能顺利回到伙伴身边，离开这里，继续追捕我了。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ConneR]"], "content": "<i>但若你对我说的稍微有点兴趣……就请往前走吧。\n请放心，我向你保证这绝对不是陷阱。看完后再离开对你也没有任何损失。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "喂！斑比！上面的通风口，我们都钻不进去，但是你可以吧？快点回来。或是让冰沙妹过去找你也可以。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "斑比？你在干嘛啊？回话！\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "……我说了，你们待在原地待命。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "队长？你要去哪？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "又想独自行动吗？不要闹啦！\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sagar"], "content": "这是命令，等我十分钟。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Alex"], "content": "Sxxt……冰沙妹，我蹬妳上去，跟过去。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lucy"], "content": "……好！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}